coration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&ldquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">O&lsquo;zbekiston&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&ndash;&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2030</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&rdquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>strategiyasida nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarni munosib ish bilan ta&rsquo;minlash orqali ularning bandligini&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2 barobar</strong> oshirish maqsad qilib belgilagan. Ushbu maqsadning strategiyada belgilab qo&lsquo;yilishi yurtimizda nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar jamiyatda o&lsquo;z o&lsquo;rnini to&lsquo;laqonli egallashi va doimiy daromadga ega bo&lsquo;lishi uchun mehnat bozorida ularning bandligi oshishini ta&rsquo;minlaydi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bugungi kunda O&lsquo;zbekistonda mehnatga layoqatli yoshdagi nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">755 ming nafardan ortiq</strong> shaxs istiqomat qiladi (ularning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">56 foizi</strong> erkaklar). Ularning mehnatga layoqatli aholi orasidagi ulushi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,7</strong> foizni tashkil etadi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2022-yilda</strong> nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarning bor yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">7144&nbsp;</strong>nafari iqtisodiyotda band bo&lsquo;lgan va&nbsp;ular orasidagi bandlik darajasi<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;3,7 foizni&nbsp;</strong>tashkil qilgan (mehnatga layoqatli jami aholiga nisbatan). Ta&rsquo;kidlab o&lsquo;tish joizki, yurtimizda nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar orasidagi bandlik boshqa mamlakatlarga nisbatan ancha past, xususan Xitoyda 80 foiz, Kanadada&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">59&nbsp;</strong>foiz, Avstraliyada&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">54</strong> foiz, Shvesiyada&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">53&nbsp;</strong>foiz, Buyuk Britaniyada&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">53</strong> foiz, Norvegiyada&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">44</strong> foiz, AQShda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">31</strong> foiz, Qozog&lsquo;istonda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">30&nbsp;</strong>foiz nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar iqtisodiyotda band.<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar asosan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">sanoat</strong> (33,6 foiz),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ta&rsquo;lim</strong> (15,4 foiz) va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash</strong> (11,7 foiz) tarmoqlarida faoliyat yuritadi. Aytib o&lsquo;tish joizki, bu tarmoqlarda ish haqi boshqa sohalardagiga qaraganda pastroq (ta&rsquo;lim va sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash sohalaridagi o&lsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqi respublikadagi o&lsquo;rtacha oylik ish haqining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">80 foizini</strong> tashkil etadi).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Jahon Banki tomonidan o&lsquo;tkazilgan tadqiqot natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, O&lsquo;zbekistonda nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar orasidagi bandlik darajasining pastligi eng avvalo nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun ochiq mehnat bozoriga va professional ta&rsquo;lim olish dasturlariga imkoniyatlarning cheklanganligi, shuningdek, ish joyida ijtimoiy va iqtisodiy himoyaning sustligi bilan bog&lsquo;liqligi aniqlangan<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/bandlikni_taminlash#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[1]</a>.&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarning bandligini ta&rsquo;minlash bilan bog&lsquo;liq&nbsp;muammolarni yanayam chuqur aniqlash maqsadida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">MHTI mutaxassislari</strong> tomonidan so&lsquo;rov o&lsquo;tkazdi. So&lsquo;rovda turli xil nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">161 kishi</strong> qatnashdi. Ularning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40,4&nbsp;</strong>foizini erkaklar,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">59,6&nbsp;</strong>foizini ayollar tashkil qildi. So&lsquo;rovda qatnashganlarning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">43,5</strong> yoshga teng. Ularning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">14,4</strong> foizi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">I guruh</strong>,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">84,5</strong> foizi II<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;guruh</strong> va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,1</strong> foizi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">III guruh</strong> nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan fuqarolardir.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ma&rsquo;lumot darajasi&nbsp;</strong>bo&lsquo;yicha taqsimlanishi:&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">23,6&nbsp;</strong>foizi oliy,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">45,9&nbsp;</strong>foizi o&lsquo;rta,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16,8</strong> foizi o&lsquo;rta maxsus ma&rsquo;lumotga ega,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">9,3</strong> foizining esa ma&rsquo;lumoti yo&lsquo;q. So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etganlarning 30,4 foizi bolalikdan nogiron.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Oilaviy holati:</strong> 42,2 foizi oilali, 15,5 foizi turmush qurmagan, 19,2 foizi ajrashgan, 5,6 foizi beva. &nbsp; &nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etganlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">43,8</strong> foizi mehnat daftarchasiga ega ekanligini bildirgan, lekin bor yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8 foizi</strong> hozir iqtisodiyotda band,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,1 foizi</strong> esa umuman ishlamagan. Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">55,3</strong> foizi nogironlik guruhi belgilanganidan so&lsquo;ng ishdan ketish yoki ish o&lsquo;rnini o&lsquo;zgartirishga majbur bo&lsquo;lgan. Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16,8 foizi</strong> nogironlik ularning ish o&lsquo;rniga hech qanday ta&rsquo;sir qilmaganini bildirgan (ularning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">14,8</strong> foizi tug&lsquo;ma nogiron).</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ish joyini o&lsquo;zgartirish yoki ishdan ketishga majbur bo&lsquo;lish sabablari:&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,5</strong> foizi nogironlik sabab ish haqi pasaygani,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">34,8</strong> foizi ish joyi nogironlar uchun moslashtirilmagani,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,2</strong> foizi ish beruvchining yomon munosabati,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">1,2</strong> foizi jamoat transportining moslashmagani tufayli ishdan ketishga majbur bo&lsquo;lgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">70,3</strong> foizi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3 yildan</strong> ortiq vaqtdan buyon,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4,6 foizi</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">6 oydan 3</strong> yilgacha bo&lsquo;lgan muddatda ishsiz ekanligini bildirgan. Ishsizlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">10,2 foizi</strong> qaramog&lsquo;idagi oila a&rsquo;zolarini ta&rsquo;minlash va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,5 foizi</strong> moddiy ehtiyojlarini qondirish (oziq-ovqat, kiyim-kechak sotib olish) uchun ish izlayotganini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ishsizlar asosan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">tikuvchilik, qorovul, qandolatchilik</strong> kasblarida, shuningdek, axborot texnologiyalari hamda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">moliya</strong> mutaxassisliklari bo&lsquo;yicha ishlash istagi borligini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,5</strong> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">foizi</strong> ish qidirish uchun bandlikka ko&lsquo;maklashish markazlariga,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,1 foizi</strong> qarindoshlar va tanishlar, ish beruvchilarga murojaat qilgan bo&lsquo;lsa,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">5,4 foizi</strong> hech qaerga murojaat qilmagan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4,7 foizi</strong> nogironlar uchun ixtisoslashtirilgan korxonalarda,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,9 foizi</strong> iqtisodiyotning real sektorida ishlash istagi borligini bildirgan. Ishsiz respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">10,9 foizi</strong> to&lsquo;liq bo&lsquo;lmagan ish kuni va ish haftasida ishlashni,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,9 foizi</strong> esa uydan turib ishlash istagi borligini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ish topishda qanday qiyinchiliklarga duch kelyapsiz, degan savolga respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">7 foizi</strong> sog&lsquo;ligi yaxshi emasligi,<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;6,2 foizi&nbsp;</strong>nogironlik bo&lsquo;yicha cheklovlar mavjudligi va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3,9 foizi</strong> bo&lsquo;sh o&lsquo;rinlari yo&lsquo;qligini bildirgan. Respondentlarning faqatgina&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">14,8 foizi</strong> kasbga qayta tayyorlanish va malaka oshirish istagini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ishga joylashish</strong> (36,8 foiz) va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">yangi kasbni egallash</strong> (38 foiz) kasb egallash yoki malaka oshirishning asosiy sabablari sifatida ko&lsquo;rsatilgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning deyarli&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40 foizi</strong> bandlikka ko&lsquo;maklashish markazlari haqida ma&rsquo;lumotga ega emasligini bildirgan,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">38,5 foizi</strong> esa bilishini lekin murojaat qilmaganligini aytgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bandlikka ko&lsquo;maklashish markazlaridan qanday yordam kutasiz, degan savolga respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8,1 foizi</strong> kasbga qayta tayyorlash,<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;5 foizi</strong> nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun maxsus ish o&lsquo;rinlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risidagi ma&rsquo;lumotlarni taqdim etish,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4,3 foizi</strong> o&lsquo;z biznesini ochishda yordam olish uchun, deb javob bergan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar orasida bandlik darajasini oshirish uchun hukumat tomonidan nimalar qilinishi kerak degan savolga respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">18 foizi</strong> subsidiyalar ajratish,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8,7 foizi</strong> ish o&lsquo;rinlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumot berib borish,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">7,5 foizi</strong> kasbga tayyorlash kurslarida o&lsquo;qitish va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">6,8 foizi</strong> tadbirkorlik faoliyatini yo&lsquo;lga qo&lsquo;yishda yordam berish, deb javob bergan. &nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">8 foizi</strong> oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlarida o&lsquo;qish istagi borligini,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">25,5 foizi</strong> oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlarida nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarning tahsil olishi uchun barcha shart-sharoitlar yaratilganligini aytgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2,5 foizi</strong> nogironlik davrida tadbirkorlik faoliyati bilan shug&lsquo;ullanishga harakat qilganini bildirgan. Nogironlik (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">44 foiz</strong>), bilim va malakaning yetishmasligi (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">16,8 foiz</strong>) va birlamchi mablag&lsquo;ning yo&lsquo;qligi (<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2,5 foiz</strong>) tadbirkorlik bilan shug&lsquo;ullanmaslikning asosiy sabablari sifatida ko&lsquo;rsatilgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning bor yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">19 foizi</strong> davlat tomonidan nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan fuqarolar uchun taklif etiladigan chora-tadbirlar haqida ma&rsquo;lumotga ega ekanligini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Respondentlarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">72,3 foizi</strong> oilaviy poliklinikalar tomonidan biriktirilgan patronaj xizmatlaridan,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">64 foizi</strong> yashash hududidagi&nbsp;nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun yaratilgan shart-sharoitlardan,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">80,1 foizi</strong> aholi orasida nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarga bo&lsquo;lgan munosabatdan qoniqishini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Olib borilgan tahlil va so&lsquo;rov natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, O&lsquo;zbekistonda nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar orasidagi bandlik darajasining pastligi sabablari quyidagilardir:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun ish o&lsquo;rinlari sonining kamligi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;mavjud ish o&lsquo;rinlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotlarning yetarli darajada emasligi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;mavjud ish o&lsquo;rinlarida sharoitlarning nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun moslashtirilmagani.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarning malakasi past, hatto kasbi ham yo&lsquo;q.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;tadbirkorlik faoliyati bilan shug&lsquo;ullanish uchun ko&lsquo;nikmalarga ega emas.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;davlat tomonidan beriladigan imtiyozlar to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotlarga ega emas.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">-&nbsp;bandlikka ko&lsquo;maklashish markazlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ham ma&rsquo;lumotlar kam.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Aniqlangan muammolar va xorijiy tajribadan kelib chiqib O&lsquo;zbekistonda nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarning bandlik darajasini oshirish maqsadida quyidagilar taklif etiladi:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">1.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&ldquo;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ushbu tovarga (xizmatda) nogironligi b</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o&lsquo;lgan</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">shaxslar mehnati singgan&rdquo;</strong> deb nomlangan logotip yaratish, ushbu logotipdan ishlab chiqarish va xizmat ko&lsquo;rsatish bilan shug&lsquo;ullanuvchi, nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslardan kamida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3 nafarini</strong> ish bilan ta&rsquo;minlagan tadbirkorlarga foydalanish imkonini berish lozim. Bu o&lsquo;z navbatida ushbu tovar yoki xizmatning sotilishini ta&rsquo;minlaydi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">2.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>Respublikadagi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">barcha</strong> &ldquo;Ishga marhamat&rdquo; monomarkazlari va kasb-hunarga o&lsquo;qitish markazlarining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">infratuzilmasini nogironligi b</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o&lsquo;lgan</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">shaxslarga moslashtirish</strong> va ular uchun&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">maxsus kurslar tashkil etish darkor</strong>. Kurslar quyidagi yo&lsquo;nalishlar bo&lsquo;yicha tashkil etilishi maqsadga muvofiq: kompyuter savodxonligi va dasturlash, moliyachi, tadbirkorlik asoslari, logistika dispetcheri, koll markaz operatori, sotuv menejeri, hamshira.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">3.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>Respublikada mavjud barcha oliy o&lsquo;quv yurtlarini infratuzilmasini nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarga moslashtirish orqali oliy ta&rsquo;lim tizimida inklyuzivlikni ta&rsquo;minlash va nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarni oliy ta&rsquo;lim bilan qamrab olishni kengaytirish. &nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">4.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>Ommaviy axborot vositalari orqali nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari, o&lsquo;quv kurslari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotlar berish, shuningdek, davlat tomonidan taqdim etiladigan imkoniyatlar (ish beruvchilarga imtiyozlar) to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida doimiy ravishda ma&rsquo;lumotlar berish tizimini joriy etish lozim. &nbsp;2019-yilda o&lsquo;tkazilgan so&lsquo;rov natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, ish beruvchilarning bor yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">10 foizi</strong> davlat tomonidan nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarni ishga qabul qilishda beriladigan imtiyozlar to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotlarga ega ekanligini bildirgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">5.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>Nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarning bandlik (tarmoqlar, ma&rsquo;lumot darajasi, rasmiy norasmiy sektorda faoliyat yuritishi, mehnat migratsiyasi) va ishsizlik holati bo&lsquo;yicha hisobot yuritishni takomillashtirish kerak. Bugungi kunda respublikada mehnatga layoqatli yoshdagi barcha nogironlarning ishsizligi to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotlar yo&lsquo;q, so&lsquo;rovlar va ro&lsquo;yxatga olishlar ushbu ma&rsquo;lumotlarni to&lsquo;plamaydi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">6.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>Startaplarni qo&lsquo;llab quvvatlashni kengaytirish orqali axborot texnologiyalari sohasida nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar bandligini oshirish mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Xorij tajribasi:</strong> Xitoyda yangi startaplar uchun davlat, nodavlat manbalar va kredit tashkilotlari tomonidan grantlar ko&lsquo;rinishidagi moliyalashtirishni kengaytirish IT sohasida nogironlar bandligini oshirishning asosiy omili bo&lsquo;lgan.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">7.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;&ldquo;Qulay muhit&rdquo;</strong> davlat dasturini ishlab chiqish, dastur asosan nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar uchun infratuzilmani (jamoat transporti, yo&lsquo;laklar, ta&rsquo;lim muassasalarini maxsus inventarlar bilan ta&rsquo;minlash, ish o&lsquo;rinlarini nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslarga moslashtirish) rivojlantirishga qaratiladi. Dastur Xalqaro tashkilotlarning mablag&lsquo;lari hisobidan moliyalashtiriladi. Jahon banki tomonidan o&lsquo;tkazilgan tadqiqot natijalari ko&lsquo;ra, Toshkent shahridagi bino va ijtimoiy infratuzilmalarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">85 foizi</strong> nogironlarning foydalanishi uchun yaroqsiz.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">8.<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong>Nogironligi bo&lsquo;lgan shaxslar ishlaydigan maxsus ishlab chiqarish korxonalarini tashkil etish. Masalan AQShda ko&lsquo;zi ojizlarni ish bilan ta&rsquo;minlash loyihasi 1938-yilda Skilcraft nomi bilan ishga tushirilgan. AQSh hukumati va AQSh pochta xizmati Skilcraft mahsulotlarining asosiy iste&rsquo;molchilari hisoblanadi. Skilcraft mashhur sharikli ruchkalar, ofis jihozlari, formalar, shifoxonalar uchun materiallar va boshqalarni ishlab chiqaradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Muhabbat Ahmedova,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">MHTI loyiha rahbari</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ilhom Ikromov,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">MHTI katta ilmiy xodimi</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114);">&nbsp;</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; height: 1px; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px;"><h5 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/bandlikni_taminlash#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[1]</a><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 15.6933px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><a href="https://documents.worldbank.org/en/publication/documents-reports/documentdetail/099052223112035849/p1783520faee9f09d0a46307d56768f9126" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(5, 99, 193); text-decoration: underline; box-shadow: none;">https://documents.worldbank.org/en/publication/documents-reports/documentdetail/099052223112035849/p1783520faee9f09d0a46307d56768f9126</a></span></span></span></h5></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: inherit;">271</span></div></div></div></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></div>
